  <h1>The Gut-Brain Axis: How the Microbiome Influences Your Health</h1>
  <p><em>Webinar hosted by Revitalised Medicine</em></p>

  <p>Delve into your nervous system microbiome and listen to a webinar recording by Revitalised Medicine workshop host Edha Talwar, a grade eleven Canadian student known for her leadership in mental health advocacy, about the gut-brain axis, her topic for a Cambridge center for international research project. Talwar has published research on glioblastoma aptamers and has presented her findings at the Stanford neuroscience convention earlier this year. She's also the director of her town's Careforbrains chapter, where she promotes brain health!</p>

